edu.cmu.pslc.logging

Class OliDatabaseLogger

  • java.lang.Object
    • edu.cmu.pslc.logging.AbstractMessageLogger
      • edu.cmu.pslc.logging.OliDatabaseLogger
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    MessageLogger

    public class OliDatabaseLogger
extends AbstractMessageLogger
    This logger will log to a OLI-style log database directly. It will log to either the PSLC production server or the PSLC QA server based on the parameter passed into the create method. It can log to any available OLI-style log database given the correct URL as well.

    This does not create a file, see OliDiskLogger or FileLogger to create a file.
